1. Demo Instructions
Include：
（1）Source file: sharekit_demo_rx.c driver_ble_demo_rx.c sharekit_demo_tx.c driver_ble_demo_tx.c；
（2）Header file: sharekit_api.h sharekit_def.h driver_adapt.h（in the include folder）；
（3）executable file: sharekitdrx sharekitdtx
（4）share engine lib file：libsharekit.so
（5）Makefile: Compile script

2. Demo capability introduction
The demo code focuses on the use of the interfaces of the share kit. 
For details, please refer to the Demo code

3. Instructions for use
 Run make (Makefile files are for reference only, users can modify it by themselves)

4. Demo result description
Run the Demo executable file, the screen prints the information as shown below
(This article only shows part of the printing information for reference only):
